          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Spectroscopic factors measured in inclusive proton-",
                " knockout reactions on 8B and 9C at intermediate",
                " energies"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "1USAMSU"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " A1900 fragment separator at the newly",
                " commissioned Coupled-Cyclotron Facility at the",
                " National Superconducting Cyclotron Laboratory at",
                " Michigan State University."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The beams have been produced by fragmentation of a 140",
                " MeV/nucleon 16O beam."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A 146-mg/cm2-thick C target"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A position-sensitive Parallel-Plate Avalanche",
                " Counter (PPAC) detector in front of the stack allowed",
                " the incoming beam angles to be restricted, and a PIN",
                " diode and a scintillator at the back of the setup were",
                " used for initial beam characterization as well as the",
                " measurement of outgoing particles"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " To estimate the total uncertainty in the",
                " determination of the cross section, contributions from",
                " the systematic uncertainties due to the choice of the",
                " cuts, statistical uncertainties, and an overall",
                " uncertainty of 5% for target thickness were taken into",
                " account. The contributions were added in quadrature.",
                " The analysis was done for runs with and without",
                " target."
              ]
            }
          ],
